value.snippet: In this work, we have analysed the available astrometric, photometric, and spectro-photometric data of 2MASS J07363415+6538548, an object located in the field of NGC 2403. It was previously suspected of being a symbiotic star and listed as a symbiotic candidate in the New Online Database of Symbiotic Variables.
